      "text": "ほぉら、{user}さん、いい眺めね？\nこんな小娘にいいようにされて、悔しくないの？",
      "startTime": 300.333343315,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu019.m4a",
      "text": "さっきまでの楽しそうな笑顔はどこにいったのかしら\n私は今とーっても楽しいのに。照れちゃったのかな？",
      "startTime": 309.4999794641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
