      "text": "（こ、これは本当に台本にあるセリフなのか……？）\n（後で確認しないと……）",
      "startTime": 319.8999794641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_10_03-yu020.m4a",
      "text": "動いちゃダーメ、私だけ見ていなさい\n一緒に楽しいことしましょう？",
      "startTime": 326.1999794641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
